$ %APPDATA%

The typical value for the folder `%APPDATA% is `C:\Users\username\Appdata\Roaming`.

Files that are specific to a machine rather than a domain go into → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData/Local[`%LOCALAPPDATA%`].

sa:

  The → Microsoft/dot-net enumeration → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Environment/SpecialFolder[`System.Environment+SpecialFolder`].

  → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData
